      "description": "To receive messages and notifications from the Ringotel platform, provide `webhook` parameter when creating an API Key. To authenticate requests coming to your webhook, map the `api_key` parameter that is included in the body of each request with the Ringotel API Key created in your Ringotel account. \n\nYou web server can receive the following notifications:\n\n- [Message](#1)\n- [Delivery report](#2)\n- [Read report](#3)\n- [Typing indication](#4)\n- [Message updated](#5)\n- [Message deleted](#6)",
